🌟 Purpose – Explain what the application does and the main benefit for the user.
Example: “Helps users generate projects quickly using AI assistance.”

⚡ Key Features – Highlight the main functionalities in a simple way.
Example: “Automatic project setup, customization options, and easy management.”

🎯 How to Use – Describe how users can interact with the app to achieve their goals.
Example: “Describe your project idea, refine with suggestions, and generate a ready-to-use setup.”
